markdownRemark.html:
I have a youtube channel.

It’s been fun posting videos. A more involved form of self-expression than instagram.

I have ones about sailing, skiing, skating, skating and scrambled eggs.

I’m only now realizing the alliteration.

One lesson learned: the edit is all that matters. For me, 90% of the effort is put in during the edit.
